{"lemma":"سِلاحِ","slug":"سِلاحِ","root":"س.ل.ح","root_slug":"س-ل-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ل-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20380","n20381"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weapon, arm","examples":[{"text":"مَدَّدَتِ ٱلْحُكُومَةُ ٱلْأَلْمَانِيَّةُ […] ٱلْحَظْرَ ٱلْمَفْرُوضَ عَلَى تَصْدِيرِ ٱلْأَسْلِحَةِ لِلْمَمْلَكَةِ ٱلْعَرَبِيَّةِ ٱلسَّعُودِيَّةِ حَتَّى نِهَايَةِ عَامِ 2021، وَذَٰلِكَ لِلْخَوْفِ مِنِ ٱسْتِخْدَامِ ٱلسِّلَاحِ فِي ٱلْحَرْبِ ٱلَّتِي تَقُودُهَا ٱلْمَمْلَكَةُ فِي ٱلْيَمَنِ.","english":"The German government has decided to extend the ban on exporting weapons to the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia till the end of 2021, fearing the weapons’ use in the war the Kingdom wages in Yemen."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"branch of the armed forces"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"armor"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"steel claw"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plowshare"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Biblical Hebrew שֶׁלַח (šɛlaḥ, “dagger, short sword”)."},"ipa":["/si.laːħ/","/slaːħ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20380","headword_ar":"سُلَاحٌ","root":"slH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saloHN","text_ar":"سَلْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A looseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flux of thin excrement from the bowels: diarrhœa."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20381","headword_ar":"سِلَاحٌ","root":"slH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K, &c.,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliHN","text_ar":"سَلِحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to the K) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siloHN","text_ar":"سِلْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to the Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suloHaAnN","text_ar":"سُلْحَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [the last mentioned in the L as a pl.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weapon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an instrument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"instruments, of war;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one fights in war, and repels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defends oneself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything with which one repels the enemy, as a sword and spear"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Ham p. 73:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a weapon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons, of iron:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Mgh, K:) it is of the masc. gender, (S, Msb, TA,) accord. to the more approved usage, (TA,) or that which most prevails, (Msb,) because in the pl. it takes the form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoliHapN","text_ar":"اَسْلِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a pl. form of a masc. n., (S, Msb, *) as in the instances of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomirapN","text_ar":"اَحْمِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaArN","text_ar":"حِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arodiyapN","text_ar":"اَرْدِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ridaA='N","text_ar":"رِدَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) but it is also fem., (S, Msb, K,) and has also for pls."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suluHN","text_ar":"سُلُحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suloHaAnN","text_ar":"سُلْحَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) and the pl. fem. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAHaAtN","text_ar":"سِلَاحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN *uw silaAHK","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ذُو سِلَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man having a weapon"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN *awuw silaAHK","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ ذَوُو سِلَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, having weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, A, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"labisa Als~ilaAHa","text_ar":"لَبِسَ السِّلَاحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put on, the weapon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, A, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a Alqawomu","text_ar":"اَخَذَ القَوْمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoliHatahumo","text_ar":"اَسْلِحَتَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, took their weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms, each taking his."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh, K) alone is sometimes termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAHN","text_ar":"سِلَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Az, Mgh.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bow without a string"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) is likewise thus termed. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A staff,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stick."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAHu lv~awori","text_ar":"سِلَاحُ لثَّوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The horns of the bull."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw Als~ilaAHi","text_ar":"ذُو السِّلَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is (tropical:)  an appel-lation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~amaAku Alr~aAmiHu","text_ar":"السَّمَاكُ الرَّامِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star Arcturus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ati AlA_ibilu silaAHahaA","text_ar":"اَخَذَتِ الاـِبِلُ سِلَاحَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^asoliHatihaA","text_ar":"بِاَسْلِحَتِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"mean (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels became fat, and of goodly appearance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, TA;) i. e. their fat became as though it were weapons with which they prevented their being slaughtered: (L, TA:) and the like has been mentioned before, [voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rumoHN","text_ar":"رُمْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmH","text_ar":"رمح"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Lth","Mgh","S","Msb","TA","L","Az"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}